{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Innovation brings with it risk traditional = tried and tested = may possibly be considered a safer bet\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Mortgageability and insurability may be stumbling blocks in the short term at least\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Will MMC homes with their innovative materials prove more difficult to market?\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Innovative designs associated with new materials may raise design issues within existing towns and villages, ignore the local vernacular and find it more difficult to secure planning consent \par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}There may be the danger of a circular argument \endash  the benefits of MMC may not be fully maximised until high production volumes are achieved, but there may be a reluctance to invest in high volume production until the benefits can be demonstrated\par
